+------------------------+
| 1️⃣ Création de la      |
|    socket Netlink      |
|    (NlRouter)          |
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 2️⃣ Résolution de la    |
|    famille GENL        |     -> family.rs
|    BATADV (CTRL_CMD_*) |
|    -> family_id        |
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 3️⃣ Construction du     |
|    message GENL         |
|    - NlmsghdrBuilder    |
|      .nl_type = family_id|
|      .nl_flags = REQUEST|
|      .nl_seq = seq_num  |
|      .nl_pid = 0        |         -> messages.rs
|    - GenlmsghdrBuilder  |
|      .cmd = GET_ORIGINATORS|
|      .version = 1       |
|      .attrs = GenlBuffer|
|        - NlattrBuilder  |
|          .nla_type = BATADV_ATTR_MESH_IFNAME|
|          .nla_payload = "bat0\0"|
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 4️⃣ Envoi du message    |
|    via socket           |
|    socket.send(nl_msg)  |
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 5️⃣ Kernel reçoit le     |
|    message Netlink       |
|    - Vérifie nl_flags    |
|    - Vérifie cmd & attrs |
|    - Extrait la table    |
|      demandée (originators)|
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 6️⃣ Kernel construit la  |
|    réponse GENL          |
|    - Nlmsghdr (nl_type=family_id)|
|    - Genlmsghdr (cmd=GET_ORIGINATORS)|
|    - Nlattr(s) avec les originators|
+-----------+------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------+
| 7️⃣ Application lit la   |
|    réponse via socket    |
|    socket.recv()         |
|    - Parcourt Nlmsghdr   |
|    - Parcourt Genlmsghdr |
|    - Parcourt Nlattr(s)  |
|    -> Extract Originator entries|
+------------------------+